# Enforce C++ dominance in Linguist statistics
*.cpp linguist-language=C++
*.hpp linguist-language=C++
*.h linguist-language=C++

# Exclude orchestration scripts, heavy UI files, and peripheral tooling
scripts/** linguist-vendored
viz/** linguist-vendored
*.ipynb linguist-vendored

# Explicitly mark documentation directories and files
docs/** linguist-documentation
*.md linguist-documentation
*.rst linguist-documentation
